  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· Original · Independent Production</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A super long post apocalyptic visual novel with a focus on depression</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/afa20f7da5779a7a63e249eab95ed867.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· Over a hundred hours of creating screen recording files, independently creating 100000+word long scripts with multiple endings and lengthy scripts</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/0e50b577b3ff7428397bd633692a0f30.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=375 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/b5e17509eda43e6bac9f918e5295ffc1.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=295 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· The game features a story of 14 main characters with group portraits, as well as over 30 top ranked characters. All characters have independent illustrations and voice acting. The author has created hundreds of character and background images, with thousands of failed renderings behind them.....</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/fcc011931b24fda07760a14759fdcada.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=324 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/a424c9db1ddd3b1bb88b07c46b1a91ea.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=312 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 15 professional CV dubbing, with over 2000 dubbing files</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/6f2eee2e57ea311f451497bdb16b3f26.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=717 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· Hundreds of dialogue processing files</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/0c00d41b309c87b534a47b94c2ea97ac.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=361 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 70+selected pieces from hundreds of CC0 music</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707580/extras/1d85f03d6115ae6c2301aa8bab2bc4a3.avif?t=1704142268\" width=600 height=772 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· Looking forward to your visit!</h2>",
